00:08:00.580 --> 00:08:03.260
And I love -- Robin knows
I love this printer.

00:08:03.260 --> 00:08:04.810
Sarah knows I love this printer.

00:08:04.810 --> 00:08:08.170
Brother laser printers are
one of my favorite things.

00:08:08.170 --> 00:08:09.470
&gt;&gt; Sarah Burnes: Write
it down, everyone.

00:08:09.470 --> 00:08:10.770
&gt;&gt; Craig Mod: They're incredible.

00:08:10.770 --> 00:08:12.070
