thing, a beautiful artifact.

00:09:02.590 --> 00:09:04.650
The goal is to do that
within about a month.

00:09:04.650 --> 00:09:05.950 position:56%
And I think we're going to hit that.

00:09:05.950 --> 00:09:07.250
&gt;&gt; Sarah Burnes: Wow.

00:09:07.250 --> 00:09:08.550
&gt;&gt; Craig Mod: That's pretty fast.

